{"tid":910954,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《水行俠》預售贏《復仇者3》《毒魔》","createTime":"2018-11-21T13:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T15:17:08.000Z","uid":212399,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"50cb7cbeb8fcb363cfdd52ead344ebfe8d8561b1","tid":910954,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"DC大作《水行俠》（Aquaman）下個月尾先喺北美地區開畫，但第一日嘅預售成績已經非常厲害，成績仲勁過Marvel今年嘅大作《復仇者聯盟3:無限之戰》（Avengers:Infinity War）首日預售紀錄，再贏埋另外兩部今年嘅大作《毒魔》（Venom）及《職業特工隊：叛逆之謎》（Mission:Impossible-Fallout）。有指因為粉絲對導演溫子仁相當有信心，所以先至有咁高期待。<br />\n<br />\n另外，串流電視台Netflix亦公佈將於聖誕節25號當日，將《復仇者聯盟3:無限之戰》上架，等大家可以睇住英雄片過節。但因為Netflix同迪士尼嘅合約就快到期，而電視台亦無權再播映2019年嘅Marvel英雄片，因此《復仇者3》就好可能係Netflix最後一套嘅迪士尼Marvel電影。"},{"pid":"4f9559eba0af3faca7b3d7759b6fea92969fd786","tid":910954,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2bff9488b333837025f935e0687b2de00a1326","tid":910954,"uid":56653,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:57:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf0e5ec79f177754614ac23287ef25c29fc79605","tid":910954,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:58:17.000Z","msg":"J出血"},{"pid":"7eb7b87edf2bf030fb96abcf5b50b19f3fe1d948","tid":910954,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6929a8c59099467ecc04f3d12c4c9d44d2fb25f","tid":910954,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"DC<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">狗</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://steamuse